the rest of the world. This book presents particularly successful projects from recent years involving various building types and portrays their development from design idea to built detail. The documented structures by Cukrowicz Nachbaur, Christian Lenz, Oskar Leo Kaufmann + Albert Rüf, Hermann Kaufmann, Dietrich Untertrifaller, Baumschlager Eberle, Marte.Marte, and Martin Rauch place the focus on their energy strategy and formally ambitious construction methods. All of the plans and detail drawings were specially prepared for the book, which makes it easy to compare the projects.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArchitecture. 7aARCHITECTURE / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)z978311062112908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2009z9783110219517oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ARTS AND ARCHITECTURE 2009z978311031900208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET KUNST UND ARCHITEKTUR 2009z9783110318883oZDB-23-DKA0 cprintz978303460119140uhttps://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-0346-0491-840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783034604918423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783034604918/original  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-031900-2  E-BOOK PACKAGE ARTS AND ARCHITECTURE 2009b2009  a978-3-11-062112-9  DGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  a